---
title: Cheddar-Crusted Smokey Cannellini Bean Pie with Garden Salad
description: We always say that cheese fixes everything - not that this dish needs any fixing! With a smokey cannellini bean and veggie filling, plus chunks of roasted kumara, the melted crusty Cheddar topping only makes this meal just that much better!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheddar-crusted-smokey-cannellini-bean-pie-6a47fa6b.jpg
